  "content": "condary); line-height: 1.6;\">Composite scoring with configurable forgetting. Both decay and promotion.</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 15px; color: var(--accent-green); font-weight: 600; margin-top: 8px;\">Selected: best of both</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <!-- What the design produced -->\n  <div class=\"card\" style=\"border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-green); padding: 24px;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent-green); margin-bottom: 12px;\">The RFC Defined</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size: 18px; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8;\">\n      &#8226; 5 memory types (Structural, Decisional, Episodic, Analytical, Procedural)<br>\n      &#8226; 4-tier lifecycle (Hot &rarr; Warm &rarr; Cold &rarr; Forgotten)<br>\n      &#8226; Composite retention scoring with hysteresis to prevent oscillation<br>\n      &#8226; Configurable forgetting policies per scope and type\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"flex-grow\"></div>\n  <div class=\"author-tag\">Lim Chun Zhe</div>\n  <div class=\"slide-number\">04 / 09</div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- SLIDE 5: WHAT CAME OUT - ISSUE BOARD -->\n<div class=\"slide\">\n  <div class=\"slide-label\" style=\"color: var(--accent-cyan);\">Layer 1 Output</div>\n  <div class=\"slide-title\" style=\"font-size: 52px; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n    1 RFC Became<br>\n    <span class=\"highlight-green\">13 Structured Issues</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"slide-subtitle\" style=\"font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n    Not vague TODOs. Each issue has Rust trait definitions, acceptance criteria, and dependency links.\n  </div>",
